", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dina_Asher-Smith\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dina_Asher-Smith\"}, {\"begin\": 751, \"end\": 760, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Daley\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.7609125024159187e-77, \"text\": \"Tom Daley\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Daley\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Daley\"}, {\"begin\": 806, \"end\": 811, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.645699341809208e-17, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The biggest names in sport will be descending upon the French capital to see their name go down in history among the greats like Mo Farah, Kelly Holmes, Chris Hoy and Laura Kenny - and there are lots of fresh faces to look out for.\", \"from\": 824, \"to\": 1055, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 879, \"end\": 885, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.719870167476622, \"rank\": 0.36480388779308043, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}, {\"begin\": 963, \"end\": 975, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kelly_Holmes\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Kelly Holmes\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kelly_Holmes\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kelly_Holmes\"}, {\"begin\": 977, \"end\": 986, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chris_Hoy\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Chris Hoy\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chris_Hoy\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chris_Hoy\"}, {\"begin\": 991, \"end\": 1002, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Laura_Kenny\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Laura Kenny\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Laura_Kenny\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Laura_Kenny\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I believe we will have one of our biggest medal hauls in our history of the Olympics,\\\" British rower and five-time Olympic gold medallistSteve Redgravetold The Standard this week.\", \"from\": 1057, \"to\": 1237, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I predict that both track cycling and rowing will win lots of medals in Paris.\\\"\", \"from\": 1238, \"to\": 1318, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1311, \"end\": 1316, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.645699341809208e-17, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So who's going for gold in Redgrave's sports to watch?\", \"from\": 1320, \"to\": 1374, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Who are the key new players to look out for?\", \"from\": 1375, \"to\": 1419, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And which famous faces are making a big return?\", \"from\": 1420, \"to\": 1467, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"From new kids on the Olympic block to the A-list veterans making a comeback, here's who to add to your watch list.\", \"from\": 1468, \"to\": 1582, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Age:26  Home town:Lewisham, south London  Olympic appearances:1 (Tokyo 2020)  Olympic Medals:1 Gold, 1 Silver  Need to know:Yee burst onto the scene after a double Olympic medal win in Tokyo.\", \"from\": 1584, \"to\": 1775, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1602, \"end\": 1610, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lewisham\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.607351643343871e-13, \"text\": \"Lewisham\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lewisham\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedi